| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1530 — Recovery Inhibition (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 82a91b43-f1d8-5c73-9b17-a27b40d5bf15"
